# ============================================================================
# Notes for Contributors
# ============================================================================
#
# - Code owners are automatically requested for review when a PR touches their code
# - You can request additional reviewers beyond code owners
# - Code owners can be individuals (@username) or teams (@org/team-name)
# - The last matching pattern takes precedence
# - Use '#' for comments
# - Paths are relative to the repository root
#
# Examples:
# /path/to/file.ext              @username
# /path/to/directory/            @username
# *.js                           @javascript-team
# /docs/**/*.md                  @documentation-team
#
